# Regression from issue #14 family: disambiguation of reverse rule in a pre-bonded complex
begin model
begin parameters
f 0.1
NA 6.02214e23
V 2e-12*f
kf 1e6/(NA*V)
kr 0.1
km1 0.1
end parameters
begin molecule types
A(a2,a4)
B(b1,b2)
C(c1,c2)
end molecule types
begin species
C(c1!1,c2!3).B(b1!1,b2!2).A(a2!2,a4!3) 1000*f
end species
begin observables
Molecules bound_a4 A(a4!+)
Molecules bound_b1 B(b1!+)
end observables
begin reaction rules
B(b1!1).C(c1!1) -> B(b1).C(c1) kr
C(c1!1,c2!3).B(b1!1,b2!2).A(a2!2,a4!3)->C(c1!1,c2).B(b1!1,b2!2).A(a2!2,a4) km1
end reaction rules
end model

writeXML()
